OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe MP for Thurrock has condemned
OL,8,Fpoliticians using Henry Nowak's death
OL,9,Ffor ideological gain, calling it
OL,10,F"completely and utterly disgusting."
OL,12,FJen Craft said that political
OL,13,Fprofiteering from the 18-year-old's
OL,14,Fdeath is "completely at odds" with the
OL,15,Fwishes of Nowak's family.
OL,17,FNowak grew up in Thurrock, and his
OL,18,Ffamily currently reside there.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
