PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FCraft told ITV News London: "My real
OL,8,Fconcern is that people will twist
OL,9,F(Henry's death) for their own
OL,10,Fpolitical purposes.
OL,12,F"There are certain people who use
OL,13,Fsituations like Henry's death to stir
OL,14,Ftension, and to stir hatred - and
OL,15,Fwe've already seen that in places like
OL,16,FSouthampton.
OL,18,F"I want to be very clear that using
OL,19,FHenry's death for political purposes
OL,20,Fis completely and utterly disgusting."
OL,26,@qD@ApmqD@Opn
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FCraft had been Nowak's MP who grew up
OL,8,Fin Thurrock. His family still live
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,FShe said that using Nowak's death for
OL,12,Fpolitican gain: "is completely at odds
OL,13,Fwith what the family have asked for,
OL,14,Fand it's at odds with embracing a
OL,15,Ffamily who are in pain."
OL,17,F"Everyone should listen to the words
OL,18,Fof Henry's dad Mark, who said he
OL,19,Fdoesn't want his son's death to sow
OL,20,Fany more hatred, tension and division."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
