OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FWATCH: Thurrock MP, Jen Craft, warns
OL,8,Fagainst politicians using Nowak's
OL,9,Fdeath for political gain.
OL,11,F11 police officers and a police dog
OL,12,Fwere injured during protests held in
OL,13,FSouthampton on Tuesday night.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
