PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FTwo people were arrested for
OL,8,Fassaulting police and possession of a
OL,9,Fweapon after hundreds gathered outside
OL,10,FSouthampton Central Police Station
OL,11,Fwhere Tommy Robinson ` real name
OL,12,FStephen Yaxley-Lennon ` and actor and
OL,13,Fcampaigner Laurence Fox were among
OL,14,Fthose who spoke to the crowd.
OL,16,FHampshire Police said the number of
OL,17,Farrests would increase as
OL,18,Finvestigations continue into the
OL,19,Fdisorder.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
