PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FViolent scenes broke out after a large
OL,8,Fgroup walked across town to the area
OL,9,Fof Portswood.
OL,11,FDemonstrators chanted "Henry, Henry"
OL,12,Fas the line of police were pelted with
OL,13,Fbricks.
OL,15,FChairs, cans and flares were thrown at
OL,16,Fpolice in riot gear, eventually
OL,17,Fforcing officers and three police vans
OL,18,Fback from the line they had been
OL,19,Fholding.
OL,26,@sD@WOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
