PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHampshire Police Chief Constable
OL,8,FAlexis Boon said some people "clearly
OL,9,Farrived intent on causing disorder and
OL,10,Ftrouble" and "while we are forced to
OL,11,Fdeal with those determined to spark
OL,12,Ffear and division, our finite
OL,13,Fresources are taken away from those
OL,14,Fwho need it most".
OL,16,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones said she
OL,17,Funderstood the anger the case had
OL,18,Fcaused, but urged people not to "over-
OL,19,Freact", saying Mr Nowak's family did
OL,20,Fnot want his murder to stir up
OL,21,Fhostility or division.
OL,26,@pD@^OUrD@HO]rD@NOUvD@QO]zD@aOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
