PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMr Nowak's killer, 23-year-old Vickrum
OL,8,FDigwa, told police attending the scene
OL,9,Fof the stabbing in Southampton on
OL,10,FDecember 3 2025 that he had been the
OL,11,Fvictim of a racist attack.
OL,13,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,14,F(NPCC) announced it would review anti-
OL,15,Fracism guidance ` which advises police
OL,16,Fto treat ethnic minorities differently
OL,17,Fto get them better outcomes ` that
OL,18,Fsome have blamed for the actions of
OL,19,Fthe officers who arrested Mr Nowak.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FDigwa was given a life sentence with a
OL,8,Fminimum of 21 years in prison for
OL,9,Fstabbing Mr Nowak with a ceremonial
OL,10,Fknife with a 21cm blade prosecutors
OL,11,Fsaid was a kirpan, which he carried as
OL,12,Fpart of his Sikh religion.
OL,14,FHe had previously been investigated by
OL,15,Fpolice in 2023 on suspicion of
OL,16,Fstealing ceremonial blades from a Sikh
OL,17,Ftemple in Southampton but no further
OL,18,Faction was taken.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
