CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1780585868
OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe police watchdog is expected to
OL,8,Freport on the case within the next
OL,9,Fthree months.
OL,11,FHampshire Police has confirmed one of
OL,12,Fthe officers involved in the case has
OL,13,Fresigned, while the other three are
OL,14,Fstill serving.
OL,16,FAll of them are being treated as
OL,17,Fwitnesses.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
