OL,3,C"Disgusting" - Thurrock MP slams
OL,4,Cpoliticians 'twisting' Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA force spokesman said that the
OL,8,Fofficer who resigned did so at the end
OL,9,Fof last year and "not as a result of
OL,10,Fthis incident".
OL,12,FMs Jones would not reveal whether they
OL,13,Fare still serving in front-line roles.
